data.name: Find the Completely Distinct String
data.description:
Your mission in this Kata is to find the distinct string from an array.

The distinct string is one that has no characters in common with any other string in the array.

```
const arr = ['track','ball','bell','trombone','zzzz','dork','flamingo'] 

distinctString = 'zzzz'
```

If there are no distinct string return an empty string

```
const arr = ["duck", "dog", "feed", "drugs", "pokemon", "alma"];

distinctString = ''
```
If there are more than one distinct strings return the last one

```
const arr = ['track','ball','bell','trombone','zzzz','dork','flamingo','yyyy'] 

distinctString = 'yyyy'
```

Every string will at least have one character, all of them are numbers or lower case letters.
